11. Pet:rabbits is on the left or right of Cigar:bongani
12. Cigar:turquisemaster == Beverage:soy-lemonade
13. Nationality:malaysian == Cigar:swisher
14. Nationality:mexican is on the left or right of Color:turquise
15. Cigar:montecristo is on the left or right of Beverage:almond-milk

